init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was the "Best Mom" mug, who was jealous of the "Best Dad" mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a very angry mug, and it had a plan.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mug was so mad, it started to plot, and plot, and plot.
